{"id":233201,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/维权网-辽宁新民市董仁生家遭到200余人暴力强拆（/","date":"2012-06-20T02:01:14Z","modified":"2012-06-20T02:01:14Z","title":"维权网 | 辽宁新民市董仁生家遭到200余人暴力强拆（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Shr4tk17Rzc/T-Erc8iYJuI/AAAAAAAAImk/NPqmGhEpoHI/s1600/%E5%9B%BE1.png\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'> </a><img border=\"0\" height=\"216\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Shr4tk17Rzc/T-Erc8iYJuI/AAAAAAAAImk/NPqmGhEpoHI/s320/%E5%9B%BE1.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>强拆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">48</span><span>小时后董仁生从废墟下救出一只小猫</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方芳报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>，辽宁省新民市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">68</span><span>岁的董仁生一家遭到暴力强拆，董仁生及其家人被拖出家外，房屋被强行推倒，所有生活用品都掩埋在废墟下。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月，董仁生位于辽宁省新民市东城街的家被列为当地沈阳晨鑫房地产开发公司的开发商品房拆迁范围，开发商因手续不全等多种原因多次延期拆迁。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分，董仁生一家事先未接到任何拆迁通知，新民执法局主要领导亲自现场指挥，沈阳晨鑫房地产开发公司负责人陈长青纠集</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>多名社会闲散人员，对董仁生一家采取暴力手段进行强拆。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当时董仁生的家人正在家中做饭，强拆人员砸碎窗户破门强行闯入他家，用暴力手段控制住他们一家人，强行将他们拖到外面塞进事先准备好的车内。顷刻间，董仁生的家被夷为平地，生活日用品、床、桌椅、各种证件、存折、现金、医疗病历、诊断证明、药品等全部掩埋在废墟里。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>强拆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">48</span><span>小时后，董仁生从废墟下救出了他家饲养的刚出生不久的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>只小猫中的其中一只，其余</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>只被砸死在建筑物内。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>董仁生电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13236622205</span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7954693370781742572?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/8c8dd51eE59BBE1.png-150x150.png\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}